{"TopicId":187200,"ForumId":20,"TopicTitle":"Mods that allow for consistent background flights?","CreatedByName":"ODGodW","CreatedById":199422,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-15T00:05:46Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"ODGodW","CreatedById":199422,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-15T00:05:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAre there any mods where I could set up a mission which would be repeated on a regular basis?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSuch as having a space station around Duna with craft that automatically go down to the moons and mine for fuel so the space station always has fuel? I\u0027m more specifically thinking about this so is there another way of doing this so I dont have to be constantly doing the same mission over and over again?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"James Kerman","CreatedById":160462,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-15T00:08:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWelcome to the forum \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/199422-odgodw/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022199422\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/199422-odgodw/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@ODGodW\u003C/a\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ve moved your question to add on discussions.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Stone Blue","CreatedById":77721,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-15T02:30:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTheres at least two that I know of...\u003Cbr\u003E\none is this:\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u002268273\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed9130491771\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/34082-part-16-davon-supply-mod-v025/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:209px;